"add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Novo Contacto</"
"guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1853
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choosing this context menu option has exactly the same effect as clicking "
"the <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;New Contact&nbsp;</guibutton> button on the "
"Toolbar. See <link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-contact\">chapter 2 above</"
"link> for complete details."
msgstr ""
"Escolher esta opção do menu de contexto tem exactamente o mesmo efeito que "
"carregar no botão <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;Novo Contacto&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> da barra de ferramentas. Veja detalhes mais completos acima no "
"<link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-contact\">capítulo 2</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1859
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"user-"
"group-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>New "
"Group</guimenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
